  "notes": [
    "Luna Internal repository was created on February 15, 2026 as a clean slate for the development of the internal base and features.",
    "The initial commit bootstrapped the repository metadata and added the solution and project files for the internal base module, along with vendored dependencies such as MinHook and ImGui.",
    "Subsequent commits added the core hooking infrastructure, SDK utilities, and various features such as visuals, combat, and misc functionalities, as well as a comprehensive set of dumpers for extracting game data.",
    "On June 2, 2026, a README file was added to provide an overview of the repository."
  ],
